      <title>摩根士丹利聘请前 Brevan Howard Latam 经济学家 Cabiedes</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/morgan-stanley-hires-ex-brevan-howard-latam-economist-cabiedes</link>
